title: Gábor Tóth
text:
Gábor Tóth (born 26 March 1987 in <a href="Kiskunhalas">Kiskunhalas</a>) is a <a href="Hungarian%20people">Hungarian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player who currently plays for <a href="Lombard-P%C3%A1pa%20TFC">Lombard-Pápa TFC</a>.
